{"tid":363352,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[無人識？]有無人鐘意聽許美靜","createTime":"2017-08-17T14:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T14:24:55.000Z","uid":106065,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3481793bd57fa37bb94b7be07aab8749db7c76cf","tid":363352,"uid":106065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"許美靜好多後生一輩未必聽過呢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但一講傾城同明知故犯呢兩首歌就好多人聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n許美靜出道時間好短，後來仲有精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但佢D歌好多都好好聽<br />\n佢把聲好獨特，因為係新加坡人，廣東話唔正<br />\n但偏偏係咁，佢唱歌更特別，有D似王菲外，更帶點傷感<br />\n試過失戀聽真係好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有無人鐘意聽許美靜呢？<br />\n<br />\n我就最鐘意呢幾首：<br />\n傾城<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UqUqpgV4M0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUqUqpgV4M0w&d=%2B%2B5F1zqjHhWQmQGNcM74LTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6faa1d0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UqUqpgV4M0w</a><br />\n明知故犯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3sv6jSE86ng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3sv6jSE86ng&d=%2B%2B5F1zqjHhWQmQGNcM74LTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=75c296de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3sv6jSE86ng</a><br />\n留下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eyxXjpPAo9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeyxXjpPAo9A&d=%2B%2B5F1zqjHhWQmQGNcM74LTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e55d0221\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eyxXjpPAo9A</a><br />\n遺憾<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zADObALjq00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2